release_note: We adjusted the microphone activation timing to address occasional recording issues.

The app primarily operates at 44.1KHz but a setting has been added to give priority to operation at 48KHz. You can configure this in the settings accessible from the i icon on the top left of the screen after starting up.
Supported iOS 16. 1.Supported App Tracking Transparency. 2.No longer needs photo permissions to save sound as a movie.
Fixed the following bug: Previous sound is imported from the second time on.
Fixed the following critical bug: Sound Import from a movie doesn t work on iOS 13. Feature: Dark Mode is supposed.
Feature: Added Mic monitoring switch on off when recording.
Fixed the following bug: This app crashed when it enters the background and then foreground on the recording screen.
Fixed the following crash bugs: It was crashed after deleting the last records with swipe. It was crashed after succeeding in restoring Premiums. Supported the new photo permission of iOS 11.
Fixed a crash bug after copying a record. Fixed a crash bug which occurs when Camera Roll can not be access.
Fixed a crash bug after recording. Fixed typos.
Fixed a crash bug when sound is saved as a movie.
